{"tid":447494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運署主任涉訛稱代署長發電郵","createTime":"2017-10-25T10:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T10:41:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f711e4fc7298026b804adc8929ee3afbf702f4","tid":447494,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171025/20193513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F20193513&d=FUvepZFKdgXg3kufk9rac8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=868c894d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F20193513&h=8077399a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171025/20193513</a><br />\n<br />\n運署主任涉訛稱代署長發電郵<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171025/large/1024ngtony1001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171025%2Flarge%2F1024ngtony1001.jpg&h=f85cb248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告梁中正昨獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】運輸署一名男主任涉偽造逾20封聲稱代署長名義發出的電子郵件，意圖令其運輸署上司信以為真，以欺騙上級。主任被警方拘控兩項偽造罪，案件昨提堂。辯方需時索閱控方資料才提供法律意見，申請押後答辯。<br />\n<br />\n兩罪指48歲被告梁中正2014年9月30日及10月10日各偽造一份Word文件，文件分別有4封及17封聲稱由他代運輸署長發出的虛假電郵，圖藉誘使上司接受文書是真的，以致對上司或任何人不利。控方指辯方索取資料包括文件及電腦紀錄。被告續以500元保釋至下月27日再訊。政府資料顯示，運署一位姓名及職級相同的運輸主任，負責新界區貨車管理事務。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC5245/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"}]}